quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  6,60,"Ko Alla woni ∆≥ettitoowo pittaali mon …óin tuma …óaanoto…óon, ko Kanko kadi Anndi ko faggiti…óon e golle nder √±alorma on. Hooti O Immintina on e √±alorma on …ìaawo nde O ∆äanninnoo on fii no toppitoron golle mon. Si lajal mon ngal timmii, ontuma Moo…ìitoyay on ka Makko √ëalnde Darngal, hooti O Yeetitoo on kon ko gollayno…óon ka aduna, O Yo…ìita on …óum."
  6,61,"Ko Kanko Alla woni Foolu…óo e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, Foolir…óo hannduyee Senii…óo On. Himo Nulira e mo'on malaa'ikaa…ìe teddu…ìe, …ìe lima golle mon haa laje mon …óen timma, …ìe ∆¥ettita on, kam…ìe ko …ìe hunnoo…ìe ko …ìe yamiraa."
  6,62,"Hooti …ìen ∆¥ettitanoo…ìe ruttitee ka Alla, jey…óo …ìe on e hoore goonga fii yo O Yo…ìitu…ìe golle ma…ì…ìe. Ko Kanko woodani √±aawoore nun…óunde nden e ma…ì…ìe, ko Kanko kadi …ìuri yaawude √±aawugol golle mon …óen."
  6,63,"Maakan …ìee sirkoo…ìe an Nulaa…óo : "Ko hommbo da…óndata on ni…ìe njorndi e maayo?" Hi…óon noddira Mo yankinaare ka kene e ka gunndoo : "Si Joomi amen da…óndii men halkagol, ma men jeye e …ìen yettoo…ìe Neemaaji Makko …óin e dow amen, wonnde men rewtaa ko woori Mo"."
  6,64,"Maakan …ìe an Nulaa…óo : "Ko Alla woni Da…óndoowo on e …óum, O Hisina on e kala ngo∆¥o. Refti onon hi…óon kafida Mo e go…ó…óum goo tuma welti…óon, hara too√±itagol …ìuray na …óen kuu…óe mon?!"."
  6,65,"Maakan …ìe an Nulaa…óo : "Ko Alla woni Hattan…óo nulugol e mo'on lepte ardiranay…óe on dow -wano kaa∆¥e maa haacaango ekn, maa ardira on senndo ley -wano dillere leydi maa bappitagol, maa Jillindira hakkunde mon, kala mo'on jokka belee…óe, watton wartindirde". Taskii an Nulaa…óo, no Men Yiltindiranta …ìe Aayeeje …óen Men ∆Åannginira…óe fii no …ìe faamira kon ko addu…óaa."
  6,66,"Yim…ìe maa …ìen fennii ndee Al Qur'aanaare, hara non ko nde goonga immorde ka Alla. Maakan …ìe an Nulaa…óo : "Mi wonaali fawtii…óo on, min ko mi jertinoowo on tun e lepte tii…óu…óe"."
  6,67,"Kala kumpital no mari √±ii…ìirde mun e timmoode mun : wano ruttorde mon e battane mon. Arma anndon …óum tuma immintina…óon √ëalnde Darngal."
  6,68,"An Nulaa…óo, si a yi'ii sirkoo…ìe …ìen no wowla e Aayeeje Amen …óen jalkita, haray wo…ó…óito …ìe haa …ìe naatana yeewtere goo. Si seytaane yejjitinii ma haa a joo…óodii e ma…ì…ìe, hooti annditu…óaa, hara immo …óon kisan, wata a joo…óido e jaggitoo…ìe …ìen."